Classification: Documentary
Genre: Crime | Lifestyle

Network: ITV ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Mondays at 09:00 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: February 18, 2013

Her Majesty's Prison Aylesbury is a documentary series which sees the cameras being given exclusive access to Aylesbury Prison in Buckinghamshire, home to some of the country's most dangerous young criminals.
